<h4><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/s5JijIt0giARYulb6_66NA">滴滴、美团、拼多多社区团购单量峰值均超千万</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-514473" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/shutterstock_261852563.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="625" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/shutterstock_261852563.jpg 1000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/shutterstock_261852563-360x225.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<p>据晚点 LatePost 消息，滴滴、美团、拼多多三家巨头下的社区团购平台 12 月件单量峰值均已突破 1000 万，其中滴滴旗下橙心优选 12 月日均件单量突破了 1000 万。</p>
<h4><a href="https://tech.ifeng.com/c/82DpfCYDihq">苹果推出限时 2 小时送货服务，仅需 5 美元快递服务费</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1386870" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/airpods-max-details.jpeg" alt="" width="1500" height="750" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/airpods-max-details.jpeg 1500w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/airpods-max-details-360x180.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/airpods-max-details-768x384.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/airpods-max-details-1024x512.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /></p>
<p>据凤凰科技报道，日前苹果在国外限时推出了 2 小时送货服务，限时优惠价格仅为 5 美元，大多数地区都提供这项快递服务，不过定制版 Mac、雕刻产品或通过融资或银行转帐支付的订单无法使用这一服务。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357461" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://www.jiemian.com/article/5410306.html">中国内地第二家「麦当劳叔叔之家」落地上海</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1386869" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/202634552.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="398" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/202634552.jpg 600w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/202634552-360x239.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></p>
<p>据界面报道，12 月 15 日，中国内地第二家「麦当劳叔叔之家」在上海启用。上海「麦当劳叔叔之家」将为在上海儿童医学中心就医的外地贫困患儿家庭提供免费住宿服务。患有重大疾病的患儿在上海儿童医学中心就医时，如家庭贫困且年龄在 0-18 周岁内，即可向上海儿童医学中心与上海「麦当劳叔叔之家」共同成立的入住家庭评估委员会提出申请。</p>
<p>「麦当劳叔叔之家」是一个全球新的公益项目，2016 年进入中国内地，第一间「麦当劳叔叔之家」开设于湖南长沙。</p>
<h4><a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2020-12-15/doc-iiznezxs7116199.shtml">亚马逊推出新服务：为买家创建「虚拟替身」来定制 T 恤</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1386873" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/made_for_you_main.jpg" alt="" width="1440" height="800" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/made_for_you_main.jpg 1440w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/made_for_you_main-360x200.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/made_for_you_main-768x427.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/made_for_you_main-1024x569.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px" /></p>
<p>据新浪科技报道，亚马逊推出了一项允许用户根据自己的尺码来定制 T 恤的服务。这项服务名为「Made For You」，购物者可根据多项指标来量身定做一件 T 恤。确切而言，买家可以根据面料的类型、颜色、长度、合身程度、领口和袖长来定制 T 恤，定制后的 T 恤售价 25 美元。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_10420309">卡塔尔首都多哈成功申办 2030 年亚运会</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1386866" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/417.jpg" alt="" width="690" height="407" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/417.jpg 690w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/417-360x212.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px" /></p>
<p>卡塔尔首都多哈成功申办 2030 年亚运会，投票排名第二的沙特首都利雅得自动顺延，成为 2034 年亚运会的主办城市。</p>
<h4>「超高清之夜」在广州举行</h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1386876" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/WechatIMG2055.jpeg" alt="" width="1600" height="1067" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/WechatIMG2055.jpeg 1600w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/WechatIMG2055-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/WechatIMG2055-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/WechatIMG2055-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /></p>
<p>12 月 16 日，「超高清之夜」—— 精品超⾼清视频产业成果发布活动于花果⼭超⾼清视频产业特⾊⼩镇举行。由⼴东省⼴播电视局指导，⼴州市⼴电⽂化旅游局、⼴州市⼴播电视台主办的「精品超⾼清（4K/8K）视频征评活动」已于 2020 年 7 ⽉正式启动。</p>
<p>此次，征评活动平台搭建的成果更促成了超高清视频版权交易，交易额高达 2000 万元。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.8world.com/entertainment/jk-zone/article/live-action-remake-of-yu-yu-hakusho-announced-by-netflix-1337846">继《海贼王》后，Netflix 宣布开拍真人版《幽游白书》</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1386875" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/unnamed-2.jpg" alt="" width="512" height="320" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/unnamed-2.jpg 512w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/unnamed-2-360x225.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px" /></p>
<p>继 Netflix 宣布开拍真人版《海贼王》（One Piece）后，再次宣布将开拍真人版《幽游白书》，并预计将在全球 190 国上架。《幽游白书》是《猎人》漫画作家冨㭴义博在 1990 年代的经典代表作品，讲述 14 岁少年幽助因一场车祸事故，被任命为解决与妖怪案有关的灵界侦探，因此发生了一连串连结人间与灵界的故事。</p>
<h4><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/98MEcUQSBU29SzjlAd0AMw">电竞成为亚运会正式比赛项目</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-698227" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/lolesports.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="750" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/lolesports.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/lolesports-360x225.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/lolesports-768x480.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/lolesports-1024x640.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>第 38 届亚洲奥林匹克理事会代表大会批准，电子竞技入选 2022 年杭州亚运会正式项目。2018 年，电竞曾作为「表演项目」进入雅加达亚运会，中国取得 2 金 1 银的佳绩（不计入总奖牌榜）。</p>
<p>而「正式项目」区别于「表演项目」。这意味着，在 2022 年 9 月 10 日至 25 日，电子竞技将计入国家奖牌榜，为国争光。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/5993531560/4582729024283177">985 相亲局下的婚姻会幸福吗</a></h4>
<p>近日，定位高学历圈层的「985 相亲局」备受关注，985 的身份对感情重要吗？</p>
<p>网友：「985 代表是不只是学历。」「我就是不介意学历的，现在过的不好，三观真的不一样。」「何止 985，相亲不都这样吗？介绍的都是条件差不多的。」</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357582" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://www.gooood.cn/the-satori-harbor-china-by-wutopia-lab.htm">朝彻书屋 the Satori Harbor @ 广州·中国</a></h4>
<p>朝彻书屋，the Satori Harbor，这是 Wutopia Lab 为唯品会设计的总部图书馆。朝彻出自《庄子·大宗师》，是道家修炼的一层境界，指透彻通达，有如朝阳遍照。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1386283" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/004-The-Satori-Harbor-China-by-Wutopia-Lab-960x540.jpg" alt="" width="960" height="540" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/004-The-Satori-Harbor-China-by-Wutopia-Lab-960x540.jpg 960w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/004-The-Satori-Harbor-China-by-Wutopia-Lab-960x540-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/004-The-Satori-Harbor-China-by-Wutopia-Lab-960x540-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" /></p>
<p>于是建筑师俞挺把图书馆变成精巧复杂的人间世——一个抽象的港口城市；进一步则引导寄居其间的读者通过阅读以及体验而能悟达妙道外物，最后能作逍遥游。</p>
<p>这是位于唯品会总部大楼 18 层和 19 层上的港口城市。隧道尽头有一个巨大的聚声罩，来到就能听到海浪的声音。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1386286" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/026-The-Satori-Harbor-China-by-Wutopia-Lab-960x720.jpg" alt="" width="960" height="720" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/026-The-Satori-Harbor-China-by-Wutopia-Lab-960x720.jpg 960w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/026-The-Satori-Harbor-China-by-Wutopia-Lab-960x720-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/026-The-Satori-Harbor-China-by-Wutopia-Lab-960x720-768x576.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" /></p>
<p>城内是善本室，琴室，会议室，沙龙，好物廊。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1386285" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/015-The-Satori-Harbor-China-by-Wutopia-Lab-960x540.jpg" alt="" width="960" height="540" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/015-The-Satori-Harbor-China-by-Wutopia-Lab-960x540.jpg 960w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/015-The-Satori-Harbor-China-by-Wutopia-Lab-960x540-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/015-The-Satori-Harbor-China-by-Wutopia-Lab-960x540-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" /></p>
<p>城外则是港口，沙洲，河滩和连绵的丘陵，它们就是大厅，咖啡区，漂浮着巨石般沙发的杂志阅览区以及城外最重要的场地—好物剧场。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1386284" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/010-The-Satori-Harbor-China-by-Wutopia-Lab-960x720.jpg" alt="" width="960" height="720" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/010-The-Satori-Harbor-China-by-Wutopia-Lab-960x720.jpg 960w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/010-The-Satori-Harbor-China-by-Wutopia-Lab-960x720-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/010-The-Satori-Harbor-China-by-Wutopia-Lab-960x720-768x576.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" /></p>
<p>通过隧道，港口大门前有一个内凹的空间可供休息，你还可以看到航船以及巨大的红帆。</p>
<p>连续的书架构成了好物港的内外城墙。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1386287" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/012-The-Satori-Harbor-China-by-Wutopia-Lab-960x640.jpg" alt="" width="960" height="640" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/012-The-Satori-Harbor-China-by-Wutopia-Lab-960x640.jpg 960w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/012-The-Satori-Harbor-China-by-Wutopia-Lab-960x640-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/012-The-Satori-Harbor-China-by-Wutopia-Lab-960x640-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" /></p>
